data.value: SELECT A.GWA GWA , FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME(A.GWA, A.NAEWON_DATE) GWA_NAME , A.DOCTOR DOCTOR , F.DOCTOR_NAME DOCTOR_NAME , A.CHOJAE CHOJAE , A.JUBSU_NO JUBSU_NO , C.GUBUN GUBUN , FN_BAS_LOAD_GUBUN_NAME(A.GUBUN, A.NAEWON_DATE) GUBUN_NAME , A.BUNHO BUNHO , A.NAEWON_DATE NAEWON_DATE , A.PKOUT1001 PKOUT1001 , A.JUBSU_TIME JUBSU_TIME , A.NAEWON_YN NAEWON_YN , A.NAEWON_TYPE NAEWON_TYPE , A.SUNNAB_YN SUNNAB_YN , A.FKINP1001 FKINP1001 , A.JUBSU_GUBUN JUBSU_GUBUN , A.INP_TRANS_YN INP_TRANS_YN , A.BIGO BIGO , '' GONGBI_CODE1 , '' GONGBI_CODE2 , '' GONGBI_CODE3 , '' GONGBI_CODE4 , '' PRIORITY1 , '' PRIORITY2 , '' PRIORITY3 , '' PRIORITY4 , A.SUJIN_NO SUJIN_NO , NVL(A.WONYOI_ORDER_YN, 'Y') WONYOI_ORDER_YN , A.RESER_YN RESER_YN , '' BUTTON , DECODE(NVL(A.NAEWON_YN, 'N'), 'N', 'N', 'Y') CHECK_NAEWON , A.ARRIVE_TIME ARRIVE_TIME , B.GROUP_KEY GROUP_KEY , '2' || A.PKOUT1001 CONT_KEY FROM BAS0270 F /* DOCTOR */ , BAS0102 B , OUT1001 A /* 접수 MASTER */ , OUT0101 C /* 환자정보 */ WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.NAEWON_DATE = TO_DATE(:f_naewon_date, 'YYYY/MM/DD') AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND A.GWA NOT IN ( 'HC' ) /* 검진 제외 */ AND B.HOSP_CODE (+)= A.HOSP_CODE AND B.CODE_TYPE (+)= 'JUBSU_GUBUN' AND B.CODE (+)= A.JUBSU_GUBUN AND F.HOSP_CODE (+)= A.HOSP_CODE AND F.DOCTOR (+)= A.DOCTOR AND TO_DATE(:f_naewon_date, 'YYYY/MM/DD') BETWEEN F.START_DATE AND F.END_DATE AND C.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND C.BUNHO = A.BUNHO ORDER BY JUBSU_NO
